prompts.frontCover: A charming watercolor painting of a cartoon sloth wearing a tiny, crooked party hat, hilariously attempting to blow out a single, very determined birthday candle on a cupcake. The sloth has a look of comical exertion on its face, with puffed-out cheeks. The cupcake sits on a small, whimsical tree branch. Below the sloth, the words "happy birthday" are written in a beautiful, flowing, and easily readable handwritten cursive script. The artwork is flat 2D, with soft, blended watercolor washes in pastel greens, browns, and blues, featuring visible paper texture, artistic brush strokes, and organic paint bleeds at the edges for a handcrafted feel.
